headline: Eastman Chemical : Axilone, Eastman collaborate on cosmetic packaging featuring Cristal™ One Renew IM812
summary: Axilone and Eastman have partnered to develop cosmetic packaging featuring Eastman Cristal™ One Renew IM812, a recycled and recyclable resin that features a crystal-clear appearance akin to glass....
